data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Port St. Lucie! This exquisite three-bedroom, two-bathroom residence, built in 2003, boasts a newer roof (2018) and a recently installed air conditioner handler (2023). Enjoy the spacious, remodeled kitchen featuring granite countertops and stainless-steel appliances, perfect for entertaining. The large fully fenced backyard provides privacy, and with no homeowner's association, you have the freedom to make it your own oasis. Conveniently located near the turnpike, shopping, dining, and hospitals, with a short drive to downtown Stuart and the beautiful beaches. Your ideal home awaits!
